            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Hercules, an altar in fulfilment of a vow. Lucius Scantius Modestus, freedman of Lucius, sexvir Augustalis, magister of the Augustan Lares, magister of the urban Ceriales. This place was given by decree of the decurions.</p>
